title: BONUS: A Message from Bobby + Too Much to Say With Kalie Shorr: Who Get's the Couch?
itunes:title: BONUS: A Message from Bobby + Too Much to Say With Kalie Shorr: Who Get's the Couch?
description:
Bobby has a podcast for you to check out! Too Much To Say with Kalie Shorr. Subscribe wherever you listen to podcasts!

Too. Much to Say with Kalie Shorr: Who Gets The Couch?

Okay, break ups suck. We all know that. But what happens when you share everything from your Nintendo Switch to your dogs? Chaos, that's what. Kalie shares her experience of moving out, moving on, and moving up.
